'bridge.conf' configures the MQTT mosquitto broker to bridge devices that
do not support TLS 1.2 with AWS.

The complete set of instructions can be found in:
https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/iot/how-to-bridge-mosquitto-mqtt-broker-to-aws-iot/

'bridge.conf' should be stored in this location:
/etc/mosquitto/conf.d/bridge.conf

Note that the bridged devices should use the MQTT topics stated in this file. 
